Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:46.80,op_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}似昭似示 命運糾葛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:52.48,op_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}堅信未來 若在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:58.26,op_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}倘為戰鬥 不惜此身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:05.35,op_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}信念交織 斷不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:11.35,op_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}此番誓言 深信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.42,op_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}滂沱大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.11,op_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}少女垂淚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:22.33,op_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰人願望 無情被奪
